Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:04.24,Default,GIRL1,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:05.15,Default,GIRL2,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:10.58,Default,GIRL1,0,0,0,,Who is that? She's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:11.55,Default,BOY3,0,0,0,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:14.03,Default,BOY4,0,0,0,,What? Whoa, it's Kujo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:16.10,Default,BOY4,0,0,0,,Today's gonna be a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:20.29,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\an8\b1\fs15\3c&HFCF8F3&\c&H0D1D54&}Alisa Mikhailovna Kujo. Born to a Russian father.\NHer grades are top of the school. She's also excellent at sports. Starting this year, she serves as the student council treasurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.04,Default,SOMEGIRL,0,0,0,,She's so dreamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:26.67,Default,ANDO,0,0,0,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.84,Default,ANDO,0,0,0,,Morning, Kujo-san. And what \Na pleasant morning it is, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:32.75,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.01,Default,ANDO,0,0,0,,It's our first time talking, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:37.85,Default,ANDO,0,0,0,,I'm Ando, a second-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:41.58,Default,ANDO,0,0,0,,Your sister has told me lots about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:44.33,Default,ANDO,0,0,0,,and I've been wanting \Nto meet you because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:48.61,Default,ANDO,0,0,0,,What do you say to having lunch together today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:49.57,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:54.19,Default,ANDO,0,0,0,,You drive a hard bargain. In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:56.82,Default,ANDO,0,0,0,,could we exchange contact details at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:00.70,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I must refuse. \NI have absolutely zero interest in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:07.94,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,If that's all, I must be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:11.30,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, one last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:13.80,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Your necklace is against school rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:21.22,Default,BOY3,0,0,0,,Whoa, she shot down Ando-senpai, \Nthe most coveted guy in school, like nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.69,Default,BOY3,0,0,0,,Talk about having high standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:26.98,Default,SOMEGIRL,0,0,0,,Kujo-san's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:33.07,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Morning, Kuze-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:40.83,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Morning, Kuze-kun. \NStayed up watching late-night anime again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:43.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, hey. Morning, Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:46.25,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.28,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You never learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:50.46,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You sacrifice sleep to watch your anime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:54.11,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,and then snooze through school.\N What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:57.93,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, the anime finished airing at 1 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:01.18,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,The episode discussion took longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.49,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Discussion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:05.93,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, like on Twitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:09.40,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nah. An otaku buddy and I \Ntalked about it for two hours on a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:10.44,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.48,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,"Insane," eh? Let's think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:19.22,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,If professing my love for a particular work\Nwith no regard for time or place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:23.55,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,is the definition of insanity, \Nthen I will gladly admit I am insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:27.21,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I take it back. You're just plain stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I see you're in rare form today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:34.63,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,милашка.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:37.54,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.29,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.40,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:43.90,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I just said you look pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.29,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}excuse{\i0} me.
