Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:28.02,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,And I can still pretty much \Nunderstand spoken Russian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:32.45,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,But who woulda thought \Nit'd lead to this bizarre situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:39.75,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,This cute Russian girl next to me fawns \Nover me exclusively in Russian, and I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:43.71,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,If I came out and admitted it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.03,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nope, not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:59.14,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Outside of emergencies and cases \Nwhere they're needed for reference,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.94,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,the use of mobile phones \Nis banned within school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:05.61,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Which means this is allowed, \Nbecause this is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:09.36,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you against \Nmy better judgment: how, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:12.11,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Free rolls end in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:16.87,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You have some nerve, pulling this stunt \Nbeside a student council officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:20.62,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Let's go! SSR Tsukuyomi is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.74,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm taking that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:22.62,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:28.51,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Tsukuyomi? Like, the goddess \Nof the moon in Japanese mythology?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.88,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Why is her hair silver and not jet black?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Who knows? Probably a nod to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:37.14,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Who cares about that, anyway? She's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.56,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You are too kind, milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:44.42,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Man, I really rolled Tsukuyomi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:50.36,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H292D28&\c&HE5F0EB&}I have silver hair too, you know... You cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.86,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.37,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I called you a game junkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.56,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, them's fighting words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.03,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:05.58,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You can't call me a junkie when I'm F2P.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:09.85,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That's an affront to \Nthe true junkies: the P2W whales.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:16.52,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You make a good point. Nobody would \Nwant to be put in the same category as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:17.86,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Savage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.21,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,And here I thought you actually looked \Nserious and committed for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:27.11,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Now, now. Commitment is my middle name, \Nand that's an understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.64,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,It's the overstatement of the century.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:32.99,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You do realize we have \Nanother 80 years to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:38.62,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Gwargh! I wanna be a hit with the ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.58,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,What are you eating, Masachika?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Super spicy mapo ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.08,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't ignore my soulful plea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.10,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,I figured it was \Njust the usual outburst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.63,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Oh, great. Check out Mr. Hot Stuff over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:54.72,Default,BOY,0,0,0,,Look, it's the student council!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:59.15,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord1.4\3c&H202928&\c&HE5F0EB&\pos(320,270)\fade(1,400)}Alisa Mikhailovna Kujo\NStudent Council Treasurer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:58.25,top,ALYA,0,0,0,,We got here late. Are there any seats open?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:04.60,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord1.4\3c&H202928&\c&HE5F0EB&\pos(320,270)\fade(300,300)}Mariya Mikhailovna Kujo\NStudent Council Secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:04.44,top,MARIYA,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'll eat over there \Nwith my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:08.48,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord1.4\3c&H202928&\c&HE5F0EB&\pos(320,270)\fade(300,1)}Suou Yuki\NStudent Council Spokesperson
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:08.01,top,YUKI,0,0,0,,Thank you for your\Nconsideration, Masha-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:12.41,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,The Kujo sisters are both so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:17.20,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Kujo-senpai is so pretty. \NI'd love to get to know all about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:20.48,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,I hear she's got a boyfriend, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:21.12,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:27.12,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,She keeps turning down boys who ask her out, \Nsaying she's already dating someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:30.53,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Taken or not, Takeshi's still got no shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:34.87,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Shut it! Don't get a big head \Njust 'cause you're friends with Lady Alya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.46,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Guh, I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:42.43,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,How come you get to address \Nthat ice queen with her nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.90,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It's cool, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:47.77,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,But she does keep snapping at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:50.44,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Hey, it's better than getting no response.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.29,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,She basically never talks to anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:57.29,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Guess that's what sitting next to her \Nfor more than a year gets you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:01.64,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,If I had to shoot my shot with one \Nof those three, it'd have to be Suou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:05.70,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,She's approachable, unlike Lady Alya, \Nso it feels like she's gettable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.67,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Not that she isn't out of \Nmost guys' league, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:14.57,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is{\i0} she gettable, though? Apparently \Nshe's turned down more guys than Kujo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:17.32,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.49,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,She is a rich girl, so maybe she's \Nalready been promised to someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:21.93,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,You know anything, Masachika?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:23.93,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Why ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.47,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Isn't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:41.24,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,May I sit here, Masachika-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.16,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.45,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You guys okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.24,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Y-Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.77,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.46,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Thank you kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:56.46,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I see you ordered \Nthe same thing, Masachika-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:11:00.16,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,It's surprising that you have \Na taste for that stuff too, Suou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:03.06,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Oh, you needn't be so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.60,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,We're in the same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.85,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:10.82,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,And yes, of course I eat ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:14.06,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I often go out to eat some on days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.61,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,W-Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:27.56,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,This is lovely, though I do think \Nit could stand to be a bit spicier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:28.50,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.75,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wish we could top it with some chili oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:35.88,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,It might be a good idea to \Nbring it up with the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Don't bring your personal preferences\N into admin matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:40.20,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I was simply joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.26,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Are you two friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:47.66,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,We've known each other since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.22,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:52.98,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Indeed. We've gone to school together \Nall the way from preschool to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:54.99,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:58.04,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Actually, are you two friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:01.78,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I suppose you could say it's a process.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:07.05,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,If nothing else, I do want \Nto be friends with Alisa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:11.62,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I don't think being friends \Nwith me will be any fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:18.38,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,So, you aren't entirely opposed to the idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:22.63,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:26.04,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,Well, we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.64,Default,HIKARU,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.06,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:32.39,Default,TAKESHI,0,0,0,,They're too shiny for me. I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:37.27,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:44.51,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,Masachika-kun, have you considered \Nmy offer to join the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:47.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Like I've said over and over, \NI'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:52.45,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,I think you would be a great fit \Nwith Alisa-san and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.50,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,And what's more,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.95,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,you have experience as \Nstudent council vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:56.67,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:02.82,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,When we were in middle school, \NI was president and he was vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.55,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:07.48,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I only ran because Yuki asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:13.60,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Elections at our school required \Neach candidate to have a running mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.34,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,It may come as a surprise to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:21.78,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,but he {\i1}is{\i0} capable of getting \Nthings done, believe it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.07,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, "believe it or not"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.07,Default,YUKI,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.95,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H292D28&\c&HE5F0EB&}You don't have to tell me. I know that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.58,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\b1\fade(250,1)\blur1\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H162734&\pos(316.364,90.364)}Oshiruko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:37.01,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,So, you two are close, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:37.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.69,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I very much am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.68,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I never imagined that any girl \Nwould want to be friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:43.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh? Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:45.97,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.59,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, I just mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.97,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,There's one right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.85,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Wait, are we friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.54,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh? Are we not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:59.35,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,No, you're right. We are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.95,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:05.37,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I remembered something \NI had to do at the student council office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.32,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.08,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H1D2520&\c&HE5F0EB&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.71,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H2C393B&\c&HE5F0EB&}Masachka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.46,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}Again, it's Masachika.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:26.59,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H36383E&\c&HE5F0EB&}Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.72,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H2B3226&\c&HE5F0EB&}Come up here, Masachka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.23,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H2C3338&\c&HE5F0EB&}Look at this beautiful sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.60,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H303633&\c&HE5F0EB&}Yeah, it's very p... p...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:41.73,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H292D28&\c&HE5F0EB&}Pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.15,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H292D28&\c&HE5F0EB&}Very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:57.00,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H192021&\c&HE5F0EB&}See you tomorrow, Masachka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.25,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H1A2427&\c&HE5F0EB&}Yeah, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:13.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I studied Russian like crazy \Nbecause I wanted to talk to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.32,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,but I don't even remember her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:23.02,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Top of the morning to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.27,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(286.545,160.182)\bord0\b1\c&H9D8262&}Day Duty:\N Kujo/Kuze
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:25.27,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(286.545,160.182)\bord0\b1\c&H9D8262&}Day Duty:\N Kujo/Kuze
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:39.37,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Perfect, if I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.58,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.78,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Morning, Kuze-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:48.13,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I woke up real early this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:51.63,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,and had nothing to do, \Nso I came in early and took care of some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.85,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You? Waking up early?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.07,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Hell must've frozen over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:59.39,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You sure do know \Nhow to pick the most biting remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:04.04,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'll wipe the blackboard in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:05.39,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:10.40,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What happened there? \NDid you step in a puddle or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:13.61,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,No. I'm not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:16.49,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Are you implying I'm a chronic spacer-outer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.66,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Rest assured, I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:23.72,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,A truck splash-and-dashed me on the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:26.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, way to put a damper on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:30.89,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Well, it was partly my fault \Nfor walking so close to the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:34.26,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,And I have some spare socks, so I'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.28,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:42.65,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You were a student council officer \Nwith Suou-san in middle school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.93,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hmm? Yeah, I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.00,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:49.62,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Say, Kuze-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.69,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Are you not willing to be \Npart of the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.85,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Not you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:55.70,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:17:00.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm not interested in joining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.70,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,But what if I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.04,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Nothing. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:28.40,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Hey, could you grab a spare sock \Nfor me from my locker?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:29.36,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:33.14,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I can't go get it myself \Nnow that I've taken it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.36,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.55,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:41.76,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'm opening it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:45.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.73,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Put it on for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:48.62,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:49.62,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.75,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Do you have to ask? \NWhat's wrong with {\i1}you{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.52,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,As thanks for grabbing my sock for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:57.72,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,It would be a nice little treat for you, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:01.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That only holds true for a small set \Nof people with peculiar taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.65,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:03.97,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nope! Very much a treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.39,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H363228&\c&HE5F0EB&}It is for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:10.03,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Y'know, I've been wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.05,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Why are her displays of affection \Nfor me in Russian so weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:18.24,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Maybe her perfectionism in playing \Nher ideal self is stressing her out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:22.34,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,and she's using me as a release or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:24.62,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So she's mentally exposing herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.25,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wait, she's an exhibitionist?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:27.63,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:30.75,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, just thinking about what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.66,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.75,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I just called you a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:38.01,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Forget it. I'll put it on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.45,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nah, no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:44.16,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.98,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What? Putting it on for you, as you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:48.98,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:54.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You called me a coward, \Nand I'm not about to take that lying down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:57.24,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.24,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm not ready for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:04.10,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,H-Hey, stop squirming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:08.75,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Easy for you to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.63,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Watch your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:18.17,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:20.81,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:37.57,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord1\shad1\blur1\3c&H303031&\4c&H303031&}"Big news, sister of mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:37.57,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord1\shad1\blur1\3c&H303031&\4c&H303031&}\N"What is it, beloved brother of mine?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.57,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord1\shad1\blur1\3c&H303031&\4c&H303031&}"\NStay calm and hear me out. I..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.57,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord1\shad1\blur1\3c&H303031&\4c&H303031&}\N\N"Gulp."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:41.20,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord1\shad1\blur1\3c&H303031&\4c&H303031&}"I... may have a thing for legs."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.40,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord1\shad1\blur1\3c&H303031&\4c&H303031&}\N"What... you say?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:42.86,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord1\shad1\blur1\3c&H303031&\4c&H303031&}\N"I thought you were a\Ncard-carrying member of\Nthe planet of the baps!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:44.99,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord1\shad1\blur1\3c&H303031&\4c&H303031&}"As did I... Curses! Never did I think\NI would fall prey to such proclivities!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:46.20,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord1\shad1\blur1\3c&H303031&\4c&H303031&}\N"Legs are lit. You go from the \Nplump thighs up top to the dainty \Nfeet down below!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.20,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord1\shad1\blur1\3c&H303031&\4c&H303031&}"I know you'd get it, sister of mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.20,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs15\3c&HE1AA67&}As did I... Curses! Never did I think\NI would fall prey to such proclivities!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.20,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs15\3c&HF3F5F3&\c&H707574&}\N\N\NLegs are lit. You go from the plump\N thighs up top to the dainty feet down\N below!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.20,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs15\3c&HE1AA67&}\N\N\N\N\N\NI knew you'd get it, sister of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.20,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs15\3c&HF3F5F3&\c&H707574&}\N\N\NWhat is with this brain-dead convo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.24,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Now, how do I solve the problem at hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:57.13,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:58.71,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.09,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What is it, Kuze-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:05.34,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, so, I just wanted to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:08.60,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H1D2520&\c&HE5F0EB&}You leg-fetishist perv.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.59,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Could you forgive me already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:13.73,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.08,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm not mad anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:22.30,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,And, uh, I'm sorry I kicked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:23.86,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:26.13,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:28.00,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'm fine, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:28.90,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:31.37,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You didn't hurt your neck or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nah, don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:37.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,If anything, I should thank you for\N giving me a peek into the promised land!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:38.84,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:39.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:43.22,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You got... a peek?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:47.97,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Wait, did you see my... p-pa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.79,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Welp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:54.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Thank you for the truly spectacular view!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:21:00.86,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H1D2520&\c&HE5F0EB&}I don't believe you! Die, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.61,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, spare a thought for my neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:11.24,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sorry! I took it a bit too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.08,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H1D2520&\c&HE5F0EB&}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.25,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:23.51,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Stop chasing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:25.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Let's talk this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.01,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,There's nothing to talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:36.52,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You sure do know \Nhow to move, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.52,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord1.4\3c&H1D2520&\c&HE5F0EB&\fs25\pos(320,154.363)}10 Minutes Later
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:44.19,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You okay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:48.97,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I would be, if you hadn't \Nchased me all over school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:52.10,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Well, that's fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:54.14,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Anyway, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:57.67,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:22:00.67,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I get it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:03.31,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm not entirely blameless, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:08.40,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Milady, please accept this offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:10.68,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnGeorgia\b1\blur1\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H162734&\fs16\frz62.68\pos(205.091,127.455)}Oshiruko
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:12.93,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What are you playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:18.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I present this to thee \Nas a humble peace offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.51,0:22:20.31,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Drop the weird act.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:24.27,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I know you love your shiruko porridge. \NYou're always drinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:31.08,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'll take it. I just happen \Nto be thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:32.70,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,True that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:36.83,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H1D2520&\c&HE5F0EB&}Want a sip?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:42.52,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,An indirect kiss scene out of nowhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.52,0:22:47.22,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So, what, if I say yes here, we can get \Nsome mouth-to-can-to-mouth action?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:50.20,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.67,0:22:50.59,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs15\bord1\pos(218.909,58.364)}Chickened\N out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:54.16,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I said, nothing beats a sweet drink \Nafter a hard workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:56.10,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I think you meant to say "a cold drink."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.60,0:23:01.98,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H1D2520&\c&HE5F0EB&}He doesn't get any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.08,0:23:09.40,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I heard what you said!
